Introduction

Tey is a South Korean singer under SM Entertainment. He is the leader of the upcoming trot boy group MYTRO and a former member of the boy group MR.MR.

Tey made his solo debut on January 30, 2015, with the digital single Dangerous. He gained further recognition as a contestant on the reality survival show Mr. Trot 2.
